## Key Design Issue: Asset-Linked Observations with No Place

Existing observation UI may be Place-detail based:

```
GET /api/places/{place_id}/observations
```

But Google Vision landmark observations initially have:

```
place_id = nullasset_sha256 = selected asset
```

Therefore, 12.60.1 likely needs a way to list unlinked landmark observations.

Possible endpoint:

```
GET /api/place-observations?source_type=google_vision&observation_type=landmark&status=pending
```

or project-consistent equivalent.

Minimum required:

```
A UI can list pending google_vision / landmark observations even when place_id is null.
```

Do not fake this by requiring a Place before review.

